{"tid":11473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［又到聖誕］聖誕卡啊啊啊啊啊啊","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T23:28:41.000Z","uid":6031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7217076970cc79a878793ed8a66d3248fd22847","tid":11473,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:59:25.000Z","msg":"就快又到聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年畫咗好多張卡。<br />\n雖然而加三唔識七寄聖誕卡呢個行為會比人屌收集人私隱，但我都仲係好想寄到出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有巴絲想要就pm我吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔識你哋，但每一張都會認真寫的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/175456_3c18d828f161ecad683ea2567bb10244.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F175456_3c18d828f161ecad683ea2567bb10244.jpg&h=81c76088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後出嚟係咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/175521_02e59868e79a2bc5ebaffdc2135d4957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F175521_02e59868e79a2bc5ebaffdc2135d4957.jpg&h=fef8c709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會再人手cut出嚟整個間條框<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/175558_03cc703c1ba71e9f9e92b1e9659ed88d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F175558_03cc703c1ba71e9f9e92b1e9659ed88d.jpg&h=2219b7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有其他樣，但唔Po出嚟啦想驚喜啲。<br />\n高登嗰邊有人想我畫北極熊比佢，我畫咗了，唔知你喺唔喺到，你未比地址我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc81b64997ddf5291460a51841b94bc6e62584be","tid":11473,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"我想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75849b8d26537893c03af3242e2df7aab5285a83","tid":11473,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"有幾張上年的淨咗送唔到出去，係貓頭來的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/175745_30cb9b8da3c320d1741cb67825150098.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F175745_30cb9b8da3c320d1741cb67825150098.jpg&h=c5e4ce09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想今年寄埋出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計計埋埋畫咗十幾個款，希望今年可以冇淨低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297018235af56a4c3df9502283adc8e13fa84025","tid":11473,"uid":6637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:02:10.000Z","msg":"想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829c95aa1c70c60d078655f417318bd20ce38239","tid":11473,"uid":21782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52ec3300dfff3cf5c980efc408cb5e36cdf5073","tid":11473,"uid":31158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"